    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Create a temp file first using org.apache.commons.io.</p>\n<pre><code>File tempFile = File.createTempFile(prefix, suffix);\ntempFile.deleteOnExit();\nFileOutputStream out = new FileOutputStream(tempFile);\nIOUtils.copy(in, out);\nreturn tempFile;\n</code></pre>\n"
